---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Children & Families – Aion HCSS">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-navy">Children & Families</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-700">Specialist, compassionate support for children and families, delivered with care and consistency.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-heading text-navy">What’s included</h2>
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Tailored support for daily routines and social activities</li>
      <li>Care coordination with parents, schools, and professionals</li>
      <li>Respite care and practical home support</li>
      <li>Focus on outcomes, safety, and wellbeing</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
      <a href="tel:01245823377" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-coral px-6 py-3 font-medium text-navy">Call 01245823377</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-6 py-3">Enquire online</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
